graph TD
    User([User])
    Vault["EvidenceVault Component"]
    Dashboard["EvidenceDashboard Component"]
    UseEvidenceMgr["useEvidenceManager Hook (implied)"]
    DataService["DataService Facade"]
    Backend["NestJS Backend"]
    DB[(PostgreSQL)]

    User -->|View Evidence| Vault
    Vault -->|Fetch Items| UseEvidenceMgr
    UseEvidenceMgr -->|getAll()| DataService
    DataService -->|GET /evidence| Backend
    Backend -->|Query| DB
    DB -->|Result| Backend
    Backend -->|Response| DataService
    DataService -->|Items| Vault
    
    Vault -->|Pass Items| Dashboard
    Dashboard -->|Calc Stats| Dashboard
    Dashboard -->|Render Charts| User